Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邀请艾拉去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有点事要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你自己把衣服都洗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要说的事是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃呃… 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次休息日的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的东西还是我自己来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直以来不都是送去洗衣店的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然觉醒了洗衣服技能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是实在无法连内衣也拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}内衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之我自己的东西还是自己洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你特地帮我洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 忘记约她了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我打算邀艾拉去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等…心急可是吃不了热豆腐的 司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次你不是打算带艾拉去游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果不是被果断的拒绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也别在旧伤上撒盐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}距离感也是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是自以为很亲近的去接触的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而会被讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是您的亲身体会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近和女儿搭话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她总是满脸嫌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长的事还是先丢在一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你说的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康斯坦斯 把邀人约会的方法传授给司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的话只要直接真诚地去邀约就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那份感情肯定能传达给艾拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位也听听我的话吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非你帮我整理好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微有点乱我就整理了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真抱歉呢 让你做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是搭档的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说这周休息日…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 我放在这里的文件去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那些我还要用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重新再做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}约会的事还是之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比想象中的要顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有重要的事要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道回去的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用导航就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想稍微表现一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用导航又没有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没有约她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上的气势去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得勉强这么没用的司不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 气势是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微强硬一点才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在不努力还要等到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时不我待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！ 还是改天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须要在今天
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上啊 GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天给司添了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 今天艾拉好像和平时不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是洗衣服又是收拾桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:06:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要帮得上司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 这周休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果可以的话 我们俩出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么样的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是私下约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去…去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不 请和我约会！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去的话就能帮到司吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是帮忙的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果你同意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢 说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是私下约会哦 真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个赌我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天午饭 你请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}切
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an7\fs23\blur1\c&H8E8688&\bord0\pos(129,36)}主题：多谢昨日关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an7\fs23\blur1\c&H8E8688&\bord0\pos(123,320)}爱母之家 白井海伦小姐\N\N早安！\N\N非常感谢您昨天抽出时间。\N\N多亏您，让我学到了很多东西，\N那么下次也请务必…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 司！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐 轻点轻点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说你要去约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不要太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然把艾拉托付给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可并不代表你工作就能偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像香月姐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在还只是个半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要认真工作才行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去外勤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你中午就吃这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有在好好吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙最近干劲满满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在意的话 你可以帮他做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是很擅长做饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为…为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 现在司脑子里都是约会的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也没法好好评价吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}约会是什么情况！这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难怪这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 居然担心他 我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烦死了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后呢 要去哪里约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个…司说让我决定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 全都推给女方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不负责啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉想去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然这种时候要去电影院啊 水族馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 绘瑠也能提出这么保险的建议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克克你当我是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说第一次约会还是保险一点比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满满的话 会想去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢…可能是海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}海岸还没开放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以现在人比较少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可以两个人悠闲的相处了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牵着一条白色大型犬在海边散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在浪花中打闹嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后一边欣赏慢慢沉入海平面的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一边互相倾诉爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是 今天不想放你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请永远不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后他们互相…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才都是胡说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 记住刚才的话不会有坏处的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满有一颗少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别瞎教多余的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的意见不当作参考也行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来 你真的没有想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 你当天要穿什么衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就穿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}私服呢 没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒是有这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是裂了个大口子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就增加花边修补一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你肯定会擅自加入一些怪趣味 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 我来修补
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难得的初次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须要好好打扮下才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初次约会…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天去玩的地方 游乐园怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}游乐园…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能想起的地方只有那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且之前我拒绝掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一直觉得那时候伤到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这回一定要好好和司一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 那就决定了哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,930)\c&H6D5B6E&\an1\fs21.5\bord0}11月20日 周五 晴\N\N在薇薇的神秘花园看到了好多从没见过的植物\N而且下次说好要教我很多东西\N好期待啊♪\N要不要买本植物图鉴呢！！！\N明天休息☆\N\N\N\N还有池塘呢！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,930)\c&H6D5B6E&\an3\fs21.5\bord0}11月21日 周六 晴\N今天香月又带我去游乐园了\N是今年的第三次了\N但是完全没有厌烦\N香月总是毫无怨言地陪我到最后\N可能香月表面是那副表情 其实很高兴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能想到那个地方…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么感觉今天一大早就这么热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不对 应该是很冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 睡醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这衣服很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从哪里开始玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\pos(503,10)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\pos(760,10)}妈妈 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很喜欢这个长椅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日记里面写过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前和香月姐搭档的时候 经常来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这里一直坐到太阳下山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看过了很多人的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘记不安之类的所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心情变得很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐也一直和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她总是在旁边睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后一次来是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一次 香月在这里提出要解除搭档关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我给香月添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这之后就没来过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不都是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过去高兴的事还有悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各种各样的感情都会涌现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还喜欢这个游乐园其他的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云霄飞车 摩天轮之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道 因为…我没坐过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一次都没坐过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那今天要不要都玩一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实这里还有很多好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不去感受一下的话太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道这样做是否是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也可能只是我自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要让艾拉在这每个瞬间都感觉到快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我经常从那里看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么小…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉初次相遇也是在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个时候完全想象不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会有一天像这样和司一起坐摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她看起来好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错…错误 这样我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在摩天轮里突然倒了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 完全不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是因为你过度疲劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先睡一下 我去拿水过来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我听说你在约会途中晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可别给艾拉添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因为这样我才说外行根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给你熬了粥过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶紧吃了这个睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我可不是为了你才去做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你请假了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对我也会有影响的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就照这个样子去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那家伙可能已经睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有艾拉在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一觉得我多管闲事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是不争气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我总是会在关键的时候搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考大学失利也是因为考试当天得了阑尾炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是也是多亏了那场病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才能进来终端服务课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后和艾拉相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样来看的话 生病似乎也不是什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望司可以一直保持着微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我啊 我的寿命只剩一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想要一直做你的搭档直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天玩的开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后再一起去好吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡了一晚上差不多都好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话不去医院也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我了个去！ 艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陪了你一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像…要没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作点
